headline: Nutri-Grain Raises the Bar on Snacking -- With Nutrition That Works as Hard as You Do
summary: After more than 30 years as a trusted snack, Nutri-Grain® is debuting a bold new chapter. As part of a full brand refresh, Nutri-Grain's signature bars now feature 10 grams of whole grains, 10 vitamins and minerals — all wrapped in a bright, energetic design built for the busy pace of everyday life.
